    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scope. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion met across 96% of operating points. Validation runs completed nominally across all 25 operating-point simulations and all mesh sensitivity levels. The assessment team notes that software fault modes in the multi-threaded Lagrangian solver were not probed, but this was not identified as a gap requiring remediation at MRL 2.",
